POE::Component::Client::POP3 version 0.01
=========================================

This module provides an event based interface to the POP3
(Post Office Protocol - Version 3) protocol.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  POE
  Socket

